Jack: Actually the illegitimate son of Andrew Ryan, turned puppet of Frank Fontaine. Frank Fontaine controls him through the phrase “Would you kindly”. 
Status: Alive

Andrew Ryan: The creator of Rapture, a city which was supposed to go beyond the constraints of society. Ultimately defeated by his foe Frank Fontaine, who aspired to take over the city. 
Status: Dead (suicide by triggering Jack to murder him with a golf club)

Frank Fontaine: An extreme businessman/mobster, whose goal was not only to take over Rapture, but eventually spread to the surface as well, creating an industrial tycoon.
He is the main manipulator of Jack, and is the main cause of all the events in Bioshock.
Status: Dead (Killed by Jack int he game’s climax)
